          <actionDate>2017-09-28</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Data Breach Accountability and Enforcement Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill requires an entity that acquires, maintains, or utilizes personal information in commerce to have in effect specified cybersecurity protections and practices. The Federal Trade Commission must enforce the requirement using specified procedures. </p>]]></text>
